          "ADD-RES": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "TTY-C"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                " From the measured cross sections integral",
                "yields of Y-88, Y-87-m and Y-87-g were calculated.",
                "The isomeric cross section ratio for the pair Y-87-m/g",
                "was determined as a function of incident proton energy",
                "and the results are discussed in terms of the spins of",
                "the two isomeric states involved.",
                "Medium scale production of both Y-86 and Y-88 has been",
                "carried out more than 15 times each using the (P,N)",
                "reaction.",
                "Chemical separation method."
              ]
            }
          ],
